Preheat oven to 160c fan.

Beat together @butter{50%g} and @sugar{150%g} until light and creamy.

Beat in @egg{1} and @vanilla extract{1%tsp}.

Add to bowl @gluten free self raising flour{175%g} @cocoa{1%tbsp} @baking powder{1/2%tsp} @xantham gum{1/2%tsp} @salt{pinch} and @chocolate chips{75%g}.

Stir to make a soft dough.

Divide dough int osmall balls and place on baking trays.

Flatten out, bake for ~{12-15%mins}